seo: Js-Forward,参数加密,响应加密,前端加密
seo_en: Js-Forward, parameter encryption, response encryption, front-end encryption
summary: 该插件用于解决前端参数和响应加密问题，通过转发参数并处理加密逻辑来实现解密或重新加密的功能。
summary_en: This plugin is used to solve the encryption of front-end parameters and responses by forwarding parameters and processing encryption logic to achieve decryption or re-encryption.
